{"word":"G2922 - κριτήριον - kritḗrion - kree-tay'-ree-on - To judge","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κριτήριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kritḗrion"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kree-tay'-ree-on"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>To judge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தீர்ப்பு, நியாயம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. the rule by which one judges"},{"paragraph":"2. the place where judgment is given"},{"paragraph":"3. the matter judged, thing to be decided, suit, case"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Neuter of a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2923 - κριτής - kritḗs - kree-tace'/2923\">G2923</a>; a <i>rule</i> of judging (&ldquo;criterion&rdquo;), that is, (by implication) a <i>tribunal:</i> - to judge, judgment (seat)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1252 - διακρίνω - diakrínō - dee-ak-ree'-no/1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253 - διάκρισις - diákrisis - dee-ak'-ree-sis/1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469 - ἐγκρίνω - enkrínō - eng-kree'-no/1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178 - ἀκατάκριτος - akatákritos - ak-at-ak'-ree-tos/178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631 - κατάκριμα - katákrima - kat-ak'-ree-mah/2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632 - κατακρίνω - katakrínō - kat-ak-ree'-no/2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633 - κατάκρισις - katákrisis - kat-ak'-ree-sis/2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917 - κρίμα - kríma - kree'-mah/2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919 - κρίνω - krínō - kree'-no/2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920 - κρίσις - krísis - kree'-sis/2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922 - κριτήριον - kritḗrion - kree-tay'-ree-on/2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923 - κριτής - kritḗs - kree-tace'/2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924 - κριτικός - kritikós - krit-ee-kos'/2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350 - ἀνακρίνω - anakrínō - an-ak-ree'-no/350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351 - ἀνάκρισις - anákrisis - an-ak'-ree-sis/351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470 - ἀνταποκρίνομαι - antapokrínomai - an-tap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee/470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610 - ἀπόκριμα - apókrima - ap-ok'-ree-mah/610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611 - ἀποκρίνομαι - apokrínomai - ap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee/611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612 - ἀπόκρισις - apókrisis - ap-ok'-ree-sis/612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843 - αὐτοκατάκριτος - autokatákritos - ow-tok-at-ak'-ree-tos/843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87 - ἀδιάκριτος - adiákritos - ad-ee-ak'-ree-tos/87\">G87</a>"}]}